打球，以她的身体素质，就靠击球力量这一招就能无往不胜，对手没有能力去调动她，更没有能力回出更快的击球。但是一旦和top20选手PK，力量优势就不明显了，短板就成了关键。 我觉得，这些问题不改善，肯定难以达到李娜的高度。"},"attached_info":"Cj4I6YjvmdGep74LEAMaCDg1NzI1MDU0IJL1v5kGMAA4NUALcgk1NTU0OTAwNjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"95 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-2953d0f910a5225b5b8983cea9648200_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1723439899.39328","card_id":"Q_662701637","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":662701637,"title":"如何用一句话或一张图证明自己围观了本届巴黎奥运会？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662701637","type":"question","created":1722042272,"answer_count":74,"follower_count":83,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[24902,1344967],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I6YjvmdGep74LEAMaCTEwOTU0NDg3NCCgj5G1BjAAOFNADHIJNjYyNzAxNjM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"92 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-6b5cf5fdfbe422267f02d9692bb92efb_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1723439899.39655","card_id":"Q_663752686","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":663752686,"title":"能否只用π就表示出无理数e？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/663752686","type":"question","created":1723089807,"answer_count":10,"follower_count":26,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/a